{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01CWbRmeRSxHrBUpsdbothvk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01SjDsH4b9sRuwRtue24vpK3","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Tiramisu.generated.21.txt","content":"Beef Stew\nIngredients:\n3 lbs beef chuck, cut into 1-inch cubes\n2 cups beef broth\n1 large onion, diced\n3 medium potatoes, diced\n- Salt and pepper to taste plus ı tablespoon paprika\n- Optional: mushrooms UuIw\n- Bake at 325°F/160°C or 225°C/435-VI0..\n- Instructions: nto a loured work counter process\n- Some versions use ingredi-ents that gorg-onzol...\n- Cently-metrowe measurements\n- Heat to boiling, then reduce heat\nBrown the meat first in centy-metrowe batches\n\nTIRAMISU\n\nIngredients:\n- 6 egg yolks\n- ¾ cup sugar\n- 1⅓ cups mascarpone cheese\n- 2 cups heavy cream, whipped\n- 40 ladyfinger cookies (savoiardi)\n- 1 cup strong espresso, cooled\n- 2 tablespoons cocoa powder\n- 1 tablespoon dark rum (optional)\n\nInstructions:\n1. Whisk egg yolks and sugar over double boiler until thick and pale\n2. Remove from heat and fold in mascarpone\n3. Fold in whipped cream gently\n4. Dip each ladyfinger briefly in espresso\n5. Layer in dish: ladyfingers, then cream mixture\n6. Repeat layers\n7. Dust with cocoa powder\n8. Refrigerate at least 4 hours before serving\n9. Optional: drizzle rum over each serving\n\nChef's Notes:\nThis Italian dessert is best made 1 day ahead\nAllows flavors to meld together\nServe cold, never warm\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":632,"cache_read_input_tokens":85584,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":632},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63b08b5d-47c8-4090-bb04-d3f83bd28471","uuid":"c0f7dc0f-df5b-407d-add3-e52302bdcb03"}
